oai_dc:dc.dc:title: A Randomized and Blinded Field Trial to Assess the Efficacy of an Autogenous Vaccine to Prevent Naturally Occurring Infectious Bovine Keratoconjunctivis (IBK) in Beef Calves
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Funk, L.
Maroney, M.
Engelken, T.

oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: autogenous vaccine
bovine keratoconjunctivis
beef calves
trial
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A randomized and blinded 2-arm parallel trial was conducted to assess the efficacy of an autogenous vaccine to prevent naturally occurring infectious bovine keratoconjunctivis (IBK) in beef calves.
